quran[5]{c,v,t}:
  33,69,"Enywe Abasuubila mulaba shinga balia abasinyisia Musa, mana Nyasaye namutswenula khukababoola, naye yali weshiribwa imbeli wa Nyasaye"
  33,70,Enywe balia basuubila murie Nyasaye ne muboole amakhuwa katoto
  33,71,"Alabakasilia obulayi ebikhole bienyu ne alabaleshela ebionoono bienyu, ne ulia uwulila Nyasaye nende Omurumwa wuwe, toto alaba naburire okhubura okhukhonga"
  33,72,"Toto efwe khwalolesia omalako kefu likulu nende eshialo nende tsingulu, mana nibikhaya okhukachinga nibiria, ne nikhubilolela tsimbabaasi mana Omundu nachinga. Toto ye ni omwonooni omukhongo omusilu muno"
  33,73,"Kho Nyasaye anyoole okhuhelesia eshinyasio abeshikhabili, Abasatsa nende abeshikhabili Abakhasi, Nende abatsokaasi beshisatsa nende Abatsokaasi beshikhasi, Ne aleshele abasubili abasatsa nende abasubili abakhasi, ne toto Nyasaye ni omulesheli muno owetsimbabaasi po"